0. HTML buildout
	.Hangman's noose
	.Blank spaces
	.Hangman parts - head, torso, 2 arms, 2 legs
	.Letter input box
	.Guess button
	.Guessed letters section (strike-through)

1. CSS
	.Set elements display to none

2. Functionality
	.array - contains n words
	.onClick - computer randomly selects word from array
		- depending on length of word, computer constructs blank spaces according 		to number of letters
	.onGuess - check if letter is contained within word
		--> If contained, display letter in appropriate place
		--> If not contained, display letter in guessed section, build out next 		piece of hangman (contingent if statements)
		--> If already guessed, display error message (already guessed letters 			should be added to array
		--> If hangman is completed - display you LOSE
		


